msgid ""
"That code causes several :mod:`!tkinter.ttk` widgets (:class:`Button`, :"
"class:`Checkbutton`, :class:`Entry`, :class:`Frame`, :class:`Label`, :class:"
"`LabelFrame`, :class:`Menubutton`, :class:`PanedWindow`, :class:"
